    17	def test_composer_carries_rebac_binding_to_concrete_models() -> None:
    18	    """The REBAC resource binding survives abstract -> concrete composition.
    19	
    20	    The REBAC metaclass moves ``rebac_resource_type`` off ``Meta`` onto
    21	    ``_meta``, so a concrete model built from an abstract source would lose it
    22	    unless the composer re-emits it.
