   520	    """Manager backed by `RebacQuerySet`.
   521	
   522	    Built via ``from_queryset`` so the custom queryset methods (and any
   523	    subclass supplied through ``RebacManager.from_queryset(...)``) are
   524	    copied onto the manager. The actor verbs are re-declared with
   525	    explicit signatures for IDE/type discoverability; the return type is
   526	    ``RebacQuerySet[Any]`` because the ``from_queryset`` base erases the
   527	    model parameter — call ``.with_actor(...)`` on a model-typed
   528	    queryset (e.g. ``Post.objects.all().as_user(u)``) when you need the
   529	    concrete row type preserved through to ``.get()``.
   530	    """
   531	
